{"tid":46704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"肥婆icon最大問題係無左原有icon影子","createTime":"2016-12-19T23:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T04:21:02.000Z","uid":5400,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00585bc43ff6e2e6179bdc94ac23b0e92d85b05f","tid":46704,"uid":5400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T23:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />        #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc <br />\n<br />\n同一個表情，原有高登icon得個頭而肥婆就有埋上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我認為高登icon既二次創作應該係由原有icon加入二次元素(e.g. 新年icon，舜雷頭icon）。<br />\n<br />\n 創作者應該要諗點樣令到原有icon有肥婆特色而唔係將肥婆扮原有icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，有人會話&quot;咁腦魔都係扮原有icon姐點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) ，問題係腦魔本身係一隻好似吉祥物咁既角色，用家既接受程度會高好多一，而肥婆本身仲要係唔太討好既形象，所以就難入口d。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我唔會反對有其他新icon上架，但係咪要諗下係咪出得太密同埋新icon本身係唔係好難入口？<br />\n我認為最好既例子如下:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc <br />\n<br />\n可能人人口味唔同，但我上面個肥婆adore icon真係麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f562099a614290963e1a2ee1a708e423d837477a","tid":46704,"uid":212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:40:14.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc 呢個幾好"},{"pid":"4096e467e57c27e982838d100efa694df2c62763","tid":46704,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔似"},{"pid":"d7775de15f1f96d088c54bdb9821c2f1363ac2e1","tid":46704,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:12:44